The paper deals with the analysis of MIMO systems with multichannel beamforming, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT) and communication (cs.COMM). The paper also discusses the statistics of signal to noise ratio (SNR) and outage probability, which are topics related to statistical inference (cs.SI) and networking and internet architecture (cs.NI). Additionally, the paper presents closed-form expressions for diversity order and array gain, which are topics related to control systems (cs.SY).
